{
  "format": "tiptap/v1",
  "doc": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Before an AI feature ships, the communications and support machinery must be ready. A stealthy launch erodes trust; an under-trained support team multiplies tickets. This sub-subtopic covers the structured work that runs in parallel with final engineering checks."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What it is"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "attrs": {
          "src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,",
          "alt": "Launch communications and support preparation phases and checklist"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Launch communications and support preparation is the set of activities that ensure external audiences are informed and internal support teams are equipped before a feature or model goes live. It is a gate, not an afterthought \u2014 the checklist must be signed off alongside the engineering launch checklist."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Why it matters"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "AI systems surface unexpected failure modes at launch. Without pre-positioned documentation and a briefed support team, each incident is handled ad hoc, compounding user frustration and engineering toil."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The four phases"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Plan"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 identify audiences, channels, message owners, and timing (typically T-5 days)."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Prepare docs"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 write or update release notes, FAQ, runbooks, and known-issues list."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Train support"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 run a support briefing, share demo scripts, and confirm escalation paths."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Announce"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 publish across agreed channels at the agreed time; update the public status page."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Support readiness checklist"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Known-issues list reviewed and handed off to support."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Support ticket categories and routing rules configured in the help-desk system."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "On-call rotation and escalation contacts documented and shared."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Rollback trigger criteria agreed with stakeholders and documented."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Public status page or monitoring dashboard live and linked from the announcement."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Post-launch check-in meetings scheduled (T+24h and T+72h)."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Key takeaways"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Treat comms and support prep as a hard gate, not a nice-to-have."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Start the briefing cycle at T-5 days to leave time for corrections."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "A single shared known-issues doc prevents duplicate or contradictory answers from support."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}